cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with deep learning methods for image processing, specifically for mammography. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
